"{\"uid\": \"bernews.com-2024-08-swd-dara-alizadeh-proud-olympic-journey\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"[Written byStephen Wright]  Dara Alizadehhas reflected on his rowing journey, from a 13-year-old who began competing for fun to becoming a two-times Olympian.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"score\": 0.9529188400843984, \"rank\": 0.04940577626267653, \"text\": \"Dara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999357280713166, \"rank\": 6.427605955900799e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alizadeh closed the curtain on his Olympic campaign in Paris today [August 2], finishing fourth in the men's single sculls E final at the Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium to place 28th overall.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995304573269, \"rank\": 4.6954290754289986e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.5976917138431858e-12, \"text\": \"Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old,supported by a large contingent of family and friends in Paris, said he will cherish his experiences of representing Bermuda at the 2020 Tokyo Games and the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995304573269, \"rank\": 4.6954290754289986e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.9813422868429327, \"rank\": 0.019012081690558336, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A 13-year-old Dara was not thinking about this,\\\" Alizadeh told Bernews.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"score\": 0.9529188400843984, \"rank\": 0.04940577626267653, \"text\": \"Dara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\", \"score\": 0.999999999849706, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bernews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never like, 'I want to go to the Olympics.'\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone here seems to have that story of watching the Athens Games [in 2004] or Beijing Games [in 2008].\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was never the case for me.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always thought, 'If I can just get to this point or that point, it will be alright.'\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The goalposts just kept moving.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I blink, and here I am [at the Olympics].\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think I am going to experience that again - I think that's it.\\\"\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bermuda rower Dara Alizadeh featured on the big screen ahead of his race    The former Cambridge University rower, who won the prestigious Oxford-Cambridge Boat Race in 2018 and 2019, stepped away from the sport after the Tokyo Games, content with everything he had achieved.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"score\": 0.9529188400843984, \"rank\": 0.04940577626267653, \"text\": \"Dara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandara_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"score\": 0.9872838776300764, \"rank\": 0.012879904799516397, \"text\": \"Cambridge University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambridge_University_Boat_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Boat_Race\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oxford-Cambridge Boat Race\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Boat_Race\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Boat_Race\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attending the Henley Royal Regatta in Oxfordshire, England, in 2022, however, led him to question whether he had retired prematurely.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henley_Royal_Regatta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henley Royal Regatta\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henley_Royal_Regatta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henley_Royal_Regatta\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oxfordshire\", \"score\": 0.9997475469567524, \"rank\": 0.00025251628156093645, \"text\": \"Oxfordshire\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oxfordshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oxfordshire\"}, {\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8902210938802725, \"rank\": 0.09650123058930472, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a playful remark from his uncle, Alizadeh revealed, that really motivated him to return to the biggest stage.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was attending the Henley Regatta that made me think, 'Maybe I want a bit more of this.'\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it's a lot of training,' he said.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went on vacation soon after with my uncle, and he said, 'You should try and [qualify for the Olympics] again.'\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like, 'Yeah, everyone keeps saying that.'\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He replied, 'Well, you are getting kind of chubby, so you should probably start training again.'\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what did it!\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not kidding - I started training again right away.\\\"\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alizadeh, who finished eighteenth at the Tokyo Games, said he left every ounce of energy out on the water in his final display in Paris.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2184, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995304573269, \"rank\": 4.6954290754289986e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started well and got to the position I wanted, the rhythm I wanted,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tried to learn the lessons from the previous races.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Credit to those guys - they were a little better today.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I executed the race plan.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy with it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bernews will be providing comprehensive coverage of Bermuda's athletes in the coming weeks, thanks to our sponsors Butterfield & Vallis, Auto Solutions, Clarien Bank and One Communications.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.9813422868429327, \"rank\": 0.019012081690558336, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}, {\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarien_Bank\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clarien Bank\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarien_Bank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarien_Bank\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#2024Olympics#Bermuda2024#DaraAlizadeh#Rowing#StephenWrightReports  Category:All,News,Sports  .\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Archives:  Categories:  Tags:  Bernews\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": []}]}"